description: Lists details of the engagement to a contact channel.

parameters.name: PageId
parameters.description: The ID of the engagement to a contact channel.

nested_items.name: PageArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the engagement to a contact channel.

nested_items.name: EngagementArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the engagement that engaged the contact channel.

nested_items.name: ContactArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the contact that was engaged.

nested_items.name: Sender
nested_items.description: The user that started the engagement.

nested_items.name: Subject
nested_items.description: The secure subject of the message that was sent to the contact. Use this field for engagements to VOICE and EMAIL.

nested_items.name: Content
nested_items.description: The secure content of the message that was sent to the contact. Use this field for engagements to VOICE and EMAIL.

nested_items.name: PublicSubject
nested_items.description: The insecure subject of the message that was sent to the contact. Use this field for engagements to SMS.

nested_items.name: PublicContent
nested_items.description: The insecure content of the message that was sent to the contact. Use this field for engagements to SMS.

nested_items.name: IncidentId
nested_items.description: The ARN of the incident that engaged the contact channel.

nested_items.name: SentTime
nested_items.description: The time the engagement was sent to the contact channel.

nested_items.name: ReadTime
nested_items.description: The time that the contact channel acknowledged the engagement.

nested_items.name: DeliveryTime
nested_items.description: The time that the contact channel received the engagement.
